          "preview_lease": {
            "additionalProperties": true,
            "description": "Echo the preview_lease object returned by the immediately-preceding decision_preview here, verbatim, to confirm a guided-review decision. The engine validates it against the live preview; you may instead nest it as user_confirmation.preview_lease. session_id / review_session_id / cursor_id alone are not sufficient.",
